snippet.title: Stickya Adventurya [Official Trailer]
snippet.description:
Stickya Adventurya was a silly comedy game. I had a lot of making it and just adding jokes to everything. The game features stickya trying to get out of the hole of doom, while encountering ridiculous types of things in his way, using farting and guitar playing as weapons. 

Play this game and more at www.eggysgames.com
